    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im currently on sertraline (zoloft) for my anxiety but the side effects r making me feel super nauseous and weirdly restless all the time. i really wanna get off the meds but i saw online that st johns wort is basically the same thing just more natural. do u think i can just swap them out starting tomorrow? like can i just stop the sertraline and start the supplement instead?",
