      "content": "okay i hear u on the serotonin syndrome thing. but if i wait like a full month after my last sertraline pill before i even touch the st johns wort, wouldn't that solve the interaction problem? once the sertraline is completely out of my system, is there any reason i couldn't just start the supplement at a high dose to make sure i don't crash? like, would a month be enough time to be totally safe?",
